testcase.name: square should return square value of a number
square should return square value of a negative number
divide should return the division of two numbers when the divisor is not zero
power should calculate the power of a number
quadraticEquation should resolve quadraticEquation with positive delta
quadraticEquation should resolve quadraticEquation with null delta
quadraticEquation should resolve quadraticEquation with negative delta
abs should resolve abs with positive int
abs should resolve abs with negative int
sqrt_heron should calculate the square with Heron's method
